This project aims to give users the possibility to deploy a copy-trading bot directly from an XMTP bot.
A user can start a new chat with our AI bot and ask to deploy a copy-trading bot that follows every transaction the target address makes.
The user then can perform some operations like:

see bots portfolio analytics powered by 1Inch apis;
sell tokens manually;
withdraw funds;
Everything writing a simple phrase!

